name: django-ninja
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "django-ninja" %}
{% set version = "0.19.1" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/django-ninja-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f52e6b5f25a83f7bda80398b3b97001011142911cff52a9dd711e63d711a36ab

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - flit-core >=2,<4
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - django >=2.2
    - pydantic >=1.6,<2.0.0
    - python >=3.6
    - python-tzdata

test:
  commands:
    - python -c "from django.conf import settings; settings.configure(DEBUG=True); import ninja; import ninja.compatibility"
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://django-ninja.rest-framework.com
  dev_url: https://github.com/vitalik/django-ninja
  summary: Django Ninja - Fast Django REST framework
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - thewchan
